Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I set up a blockade at the tollgate just like you said, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really saying someone died in their car while driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it looks like he was strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, wouldn't the culprit have to be someone riding with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's the funny thing. The driver was the only one on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you go about strangling a driver while they're driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Heiji said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the body was still warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit must be in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Shinichi suggested that, if we block the tollgate\N1KM ahead of the scene, we could capture them for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said they'd narrow down the suspects\Nand disappeared into the line of cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Narrow down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can we do that with nearly a hundred cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this way we'll get to see them in action, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The famous high-school detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are only three cars that are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A desperate crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A splendid revival reverses the conclusion to a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us reason our way through both the case and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it that Ran truly wants to ask Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are only three cars that are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest of the cars will get in the way, so it's OK to let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Three of them"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What we learned from the condition of the body was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quite clear that the victim was strangled while driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit must have brought their car near the\Nvictim's while it was moving and done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's natural to think along these lines, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what method the culprit used...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must have prepared it in advance and gotten on\Nthe highway at roughly the same time as the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you're saying is there were only three cars that got on\Nthe highway from the same interchange as the victim, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could ask them to show you the tickets\Nthey received at the interchange, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These days, with ETC (electronic toll collection), they have systems\Nthat let you through the tollgate without getting a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim got on the highway from the same interchange we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ETC machine there has been\Nout of order since just before noon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had to use the general gate and get a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you could narrow it down to only the\Npeople who had tickets from that interchange, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, when we checked the victim's ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered he'd got on the highway an hour before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An hour before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He likely stopped to eat or something\Nat one of the rest stops along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While many cars got onto the highway at the\Nsame time and from the same interchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For those that parked at the rest stop for an hour and\Nwere, for some reason, driving near the victim's car...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were only three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car with the victim's body in it is stopped\Na kilometer back with its hazard lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call forensics and have them examine it in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, why don't we go over to the suspects' cars and question them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, let's have our dinner date some another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth are these kids?PP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Heiji, why is Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wearing your hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked if he could borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you like hats, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems weird, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a change of image, a change of image.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because the bad guys Kudou is after think he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it'd at least help to hide his face, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long will his body stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudou said he'd probably last for half a day or so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was he right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the drivers of the three suspicious cars I mentioned earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:17.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,All I was doing was going on a drive on the highway with Gunpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You see, the one that died, Gunpei, was my boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:20.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}\hMizuhashi Riko (35)\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Going on a drive?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were driving your own car, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunpei and I both loved to drive our cars. Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and the victim arranged to visit the rest stop before you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunpei said he was suddenly feeling tired\Nand asked if he could rest for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With no other choice, I killed some time at the\Nrest stop restaurant and then woke him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what were you two doing at the rest stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:56.35,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I got hungry, so I went into the rest stop to have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:56.35,CharCard2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}\hChuuda Atsuo (34)\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:04.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I suddenly had a stomachache hit me while driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:06.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So I went to the bathroom at the rest stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:06.82,CharCard3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Shimodori Futoshi (48)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard someone died in their car, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with me whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And me, too - it's likely not someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of you knew Gunpei very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the leader of Gunpei's rival team, the Black Stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're the father of Akira - one of Gunpei's team\Nmembers that died in a road accident not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying the victim was Furuki Gunpei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:44.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The former leader of that street racing gang that\Nhangs out it western Tokyo, the Red Comets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:44.31,CharCard4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}\hFuruki Gunpei (32)\h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stopped dyeing his hair and shaved off his beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention the Red Comets...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard their leader took responsibility for\Nsome accident and ended up resigning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was to be his last drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was just taking the car out for a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nevertheless, this man came up behind Gunpei's\Ncar and started insistently flashing his passing lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he could never beat Gunpei in a real\Nrace, so he was probably doing it out of spite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that bastard going and talking shit like he's going\Nto quit after his winning streak, I tried to piss him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when he didn't get into it, I just ended up passing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like he was enjoying his friendly drive\Nwith the woman I thought broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy sounded his horn a whole bunch of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because, after that guy passed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was right behind Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he suddenly reduced speed, I sounded\Nthe horn instinctively to prevent a collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, thinking he was going into the passing lane to\Nchase the car that passed him, I sounded my horn again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the day of my son's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:09:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} swore to me he'd retire from street racing, so I was upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was immediately after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s driving became really erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in the passing lane but didn't try to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was moving sluggishly, and he started\Nscraping the car against the guardrail...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what triggered my quick reflexes,\Nand using my exceptional judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I moved in front of his car...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to slow it to a stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I discovered the strangled body of the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, I seem to recall that being Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you guys were the first to find the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought Gunpei was driving strangely also!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, at the time, I immediately\Nstopped behind him and rushed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if what the three of them just said is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem they had the chance to strangle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for the next step, could you show me where\Nthe victim's car was, my young detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And me too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for you, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have the blockade on the tollbooth taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then stay here with these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha, you stay here with her for now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be back in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi's leaving me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have things to ask you and tell you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So wait for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if my deduction's correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That what we would like to ask each other is one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all this sweet talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} comes back, don't let him go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was really like this while the car was going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hard to believe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What caught my eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are these thin scratches on the window molding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It almost looks like something was pulling on it from outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're saying someone fastened\Nsomething like a cord around the victim's neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And pulled it while driving in a different car?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, that's impossible. Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they used the strength of the car to pull the cord...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His neck would be broken before he had been asphyxiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what has me puzzled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is the window all the way down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because he's a heavy smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ashtray is full of spent cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you open the window to let the smoke out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At high speed, the wind is pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd only be able to keep the window down just a bit out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how much is "a bit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just enough to let the smoke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two holes drilled into bottom of the window glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I have it, Kudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick the culprit used!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drug may not be effective for much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't give you an exact figure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But guessing based on my previous data\Nfrom giving the drug to Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be unusual for him to be having those spasms soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though she said I'd build up resistance to the drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even been 4 hours yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since it's Shinichi, he'll come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the spasms start, he'll have around\N30 minutes before he changes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think before you speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the efficacy of the drug shortened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time between when spasms start and\Nwhen he turns into a child is also shortened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even say with certainty that he has ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he hasn't realized that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His secret will be out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you had a slight cold, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's best if we have you examined by a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be after we solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please bring those three people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He knows who the criminal is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll bring these three right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take you in my car, so come please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} - let's go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi said he'd be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he always try to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we don't want to get in the way of their deductions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was strangled?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, wouldn't it have been impossible for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as you ensured Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did something while driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ensure he does something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With him driving so fast, what are you proposing we could have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we just say that it was possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those openings at the bottom of the driver's side window...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you use those two small holes, you can manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mechanism is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you take both ends of a thin, strong fishing line and\Npass them inside through the two holes in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, after passing both ends from\Nbehind through the gap in the headrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You slip one end through the back of Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nnecktie, and tie the other end to the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, if you make him open the power window...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The line will be automatically pulled - effectively strangling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the auto button on the driver's side, the\Nwindow won't stop until it's completely open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, kid, how did we make him open the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I did was come up behind his car\Nand overtake him in the passing lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, all I did was sound my horn on two occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First was when Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car suddenly slowed down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the second time was when he started chasing Chuuda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This doesn't have anything to do with me, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You slowed down, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were driving in front of him and reduced your speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was forced to as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, thinking something was wrong, he got into the passing lane...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And came up alongside your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I yelled at him to lower the window or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that you said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that was required was that you face him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, with an anxious look, feign crying for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd lower the window to catch what you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who used this trick on him was his girlfriend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were able to setup this trick while he was asleep at the rest stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he told you to wake him, he'd already\Ngiven you the key to his car, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She got him to take a sleeping pill beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably made the holes before you and he started driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Gunpei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} habitually left the window slightly open in order to let\Nhis cigarette smoke out, the holes would be hidden from view.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's your proof that I did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After we discovered the body, you went by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you drove directly to the tollbooth inside your own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if we investigate your car, I'm sure that we'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You rushed over to the body before we got there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when you severed and removed the fishing line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you also made sure Gunpei san was sound\Nasleep during his nap by using chloroform on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you woke him with the scent of ammonia or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of this could be stored in your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fishing line...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chloroform, the ammonia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I expected the police to question me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You cute little detective boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought you'd see through my trick in an instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as these young detectives said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one sent Gunpei to the grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was still holding the steering wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died with his hands clinched to the steering wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Akira did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean my son, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ditched Gunpei and started dating Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just after Gunpei lost a crucial battle against Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I like whoever's the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his reputation trashed and then getting dumped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had to arrange for that battle in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were no kind of conditions for a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even so, Gunpei challenged Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As might be expected, Akira's car lost traction on\Nthe wet road and fell to the depths of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, weren't they both taking an equal risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he took up the challenge, he accepted that risk as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The challenger too, he accepted the\Nresponsibility and did the decent thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy? Decent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just a pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I think as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you start racing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't stop until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I had to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This cold-hearted red devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe he truly regretted what he had done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you possibly know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up above the instrument panel in front of the driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are cigarettes and a lighter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given the dampness of the cigarette filters in the ashtray...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's clear he was smoking before he was strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he leaned forward to get the cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he have noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That something strange was around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he just cut the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he had already resolved himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That his crimes could only be atoned for with his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He already... knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonetheless, I would never consider sympathizing with his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you had killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He made you into a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something I cannot accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have made that choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the wrong... answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, get an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't go to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get you to the hospital so they\Ncan treat you and you can get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You promised to tell me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The answer to your deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
